longBusinessSummary: Nibe Limited engages in the fabrication and machining of components business in India and internationally. It manufactures structures, sub-assemblies, and assemblies of mobile weapon launchers; structural and engineering systems for naval applications; electrical and electronic box assemblies, such as console panels. The company also offers e-cycles, e-scooters, and e-rickshaws; and related motors. In addition, it engages in the research and development of lithium-ion battery packs and solutions. The company was formerly known as Kavita Fabrics Limited and changed its name to Nibe Limited in July 2020. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Pune, India.
